# Adding New Features

1. New view: add viewState, child model, setChildSizes entry, Update/View/handleKey cases
2. New async op: add Msg type and Cmd factory in messages.go; handle Msg in root Update
3. New shortcut: add case in handleKey (viewTable), update renderFooter and help
4. Toast: m.table.addToast(msg, "success"|"error"|"info")
5. Inline op: m.table.busyVMs[name] = busyInfo{operation, startTime}; return cmd with inline:true
